{"id":447,"ayahs":[{"number":25,"arabic":"مَا لَكُمْ لَا تَنَاصَرُونَ","translation":"“How is it that [now] you cannot succour one another?”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3813.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":28478,"position":1,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"\"(বলা হবে) কি","audioUrl":"wbw/037_025_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28479,"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের হলো (যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/037_025_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28480,"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/037_025_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28481,"position":4,"arabic":"تَنَاصَرُونَ","translation":"তোমরা পরস্পরে সাহায্য করছো\"","audioUrl":"wbw/037_025_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28482,"position":5,"arabic":"٢٥","translation":"(২৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":26,"arabic":"بَلْ هُمُ ٱلْيَوْمَ مُسْتَسْلِمُونَ","translation":"Nay, but on that Day they would willingly surrender [to God];","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3814.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":29390,"position":1,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/037_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29391,"position":2,"arabic":"هُمُ","translation":"তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/037_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29392,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمَ","translation":"আজ","audioUrl":"wbw/037_026_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29393,"position":4,"arabic":"مُسْتَسْلِمُونَ","translation":"আত্মসমর্পণকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/037_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29394,"position":5,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"وَأَقْبَلَ بَعْضُهُمْ عَلَىٰ بَعْضٍۢ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","translation":"but [since it will be too late,] they will turn upon one another, demanding of each other [to relieve them of the burden of their past sins].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3815.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":30383,"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَقْبَلَ","translation":"এবং মুখোমুখী হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_027_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30384,"position":2,"arabic":"بَعْضُهُمْ","translation":"তাদের একে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30385,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30386,"position":4,"arabic":"بَعْضٍۢ","translation":"অপরের","audioUrl":"wbw/037_027_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30387,"position":5,"arabic":"يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","translation":"তারা পরস্পরে জিজ্ঞাসাবাদ করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_027_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30388,"position":6,"arabic":"٢٧","translation":"(২৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":28,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟ إِنَّكُمْ كُنتُمْ تَأْتُونَنَا عَنِ ٱلْيَمِينِ","translation":"Some [of them] will say: “Behold, you were wont to approach us [deceptively] from the right!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3816.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":31395,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","translation":"(অনুসারীরা) বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_028_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31396,"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّكُمْ","translation":"\"তোমরা নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/037_028_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31397,"position":3,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/037_028_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31398,"position":4,"arabic":"تَأْتُونَنَا","translation":"কাছে আসতে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_028_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31399,"position":5,"arabic":"عَنِ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_028_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31400,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْيَمِينِ","translation":"ডানদিক (অর্থাৎ শক্তি নিয়ে)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/037_028_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31401,"position":7,"arabic":"٢٨","translation":"(২৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":29,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ بَل لَّمْ تَكُونُوا۟ مُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"[To which] the others will reply: “Nay, you yourselves were bereft of all faith!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3817.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":32343,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"(নেতারা) বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_029_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32344,"position":2,"arabic":"بَل","translation":"\"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/037_029_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32345,"position":3,"arabic":"لَّمْ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/037_029_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32346,"position":4,"arabic":"تَكُونُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_029_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32347,"position":5,"arabic":"مُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"মু'মিন","audioUrl":"wbw/037_029_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32348,"position":6,"arabic":"٢٩","translation":"(২৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":30,"arabic":"وَمَا كَانَ لَنَا عَلَيْكُم مِّن سُلْطَٰنٍۭ ۖ بَلْ كُنتُمْ قَوْمًۭا طَٰغِينَ","translation":"Moreover, we had no power at all over you: nay, you were people filled with overweening arrogance!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3818.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":33203,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33204,"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33205,"position":3,"arabic":"لَنَا","translation":"আমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33206,"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُم","translation":"তোমাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33207,"position":5,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33208,"position":6,"arabic":"سُلْطَـٰنٍۭ ۖ","translation":"কর্তৃত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33210,"position":7,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33211,"position":8,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33212,"position":9,"arabic":"قَوْمًۭا","translation":"সম্প্রদায়","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33213,"position":10,"arabic":"طَـٰغِينَ","translation":"অবাধ্য","audioUrl":"wbw/037_030_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33214,"position":11,"arabic":"٣٠","translation":"(৩০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":31,"arabic":"فَحَقَّ عَلَيْنَا قَوْلُ رَبِّنَآ ۖ إِنَّا لَذَآئِقُونَ","translation":"But now our Sustainer’s word has come true against us [as well]: verily, we are bound to taste [the fruit of our sins].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3819.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":34262,"position":1,"arabic":"فَحَقَّ","translation":"সুতরাং সত্য হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/037_031_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34263,"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْنَا","translation":"আমাদের বিরুদ্ধে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_031_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34264,"position":3,"arabic":"قَوْلُ","translation":"কথা","audioUrl":"wbw/037_031_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34265,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّنَآ ۖ","translation":"আমাদের রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/037_031_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34267,"position":5,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/037_031_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34268,"position":6,"arabic":"لَذَآئِقُونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই (শাস্তির) স্বাদ ভোগ করতে হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_031_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34269,"position":7,"arabic":"٣١","translation":"(৩১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":32,"arabic":"فَأَغْوَيْنَٰكُمْ إِنَّا كُنَّا غَٰوِينَ","translation":"So then, [if it be true that] we have caused you to err grievously - behold, we ourselves had been lost in grievous error!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3820.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":35120,"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَغْوَيْنَـٰكُمْ","translation":"কারণ তোমাদেরকে আমরা বিভ্রান্ত করেছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/037_032_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35121,"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/037_032_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35122,"position":3,"arabic":"كُنَّا","translation":"ছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/037_032_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35123,"position":4,"arabic":"غَـٰوِينَ","translation":"বিভ্রান্ত\"","audioUrl":"wbw/037_032_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35124,"position":5,"arabic":"٣٢","translation":"(৩২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":33,"arabic":"فَإِنَّهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍۢ فِى ٱلْعَذَابِ مُشْتَرِكُونَ","translation":"And, verily, on that Day they all will share in their common suffering.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3821.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":36032,"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِنَّهُمْ","translation":"অতঃপর তারা নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/037_033_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36033,"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","translation":"সেদিন","audioUrl":"wbw/037_033_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36034,"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_033_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36035,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْعَذَابِ","translation":"শাস্তির","audioUrl":"wbw/037_033_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36036,"position":5,"arabic":"مُشْتَرِكُونَ","translation":"সম অংশীদার হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_033_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36037,"position":6,"arabic":"٣٣","translation":"(৩৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":34,"arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَفْعَلُ بِٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","translation":"Verily, thus shall We deal with all who were lost in sin:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3822.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":36842,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/037_034_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36843,"position":2,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এরূপই","audioUrl":"wbw/037_034_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36844,"position":3,"arabic":"نَفْعَلُ","translation":"আমরা করি","audioUrl":"wbw/037_034_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36845,"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","translation":"অপরাধীদের সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_034_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36846,"position":5,"arabic":"٣٤","translation":"(৩৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":35,"arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ كَانُوٓا۟ إِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمْ لَآ إِلَٰهَ إِلَّا ٱللَّهُ يَسْتَكْبِرُونَ","translation":"for, behold, whenever they were told, “There is no deity save God,” they would glory in their arrogance","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3823.mp3","surahId":37,"words":[{"id":37649,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ","translation":"তারা নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/037_035_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37650,"position":2,"arabic":"كَانُوٓا۟","translation":"ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/037_035_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37651,"position":3,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/037_035_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37652,"position":4,"arabic":"قِيلَ","translation":"বলা হতো","audioUrl":"wbw/037_035_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37653,"position":5,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/037_035_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37654,"position":6,"arabic":"لَآ","translation":"\"নাই","audioUrl":"wbw/037_035_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37655,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَـٰهَ","translation":"কোনো ইলাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/037_035_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37656,"position":8,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/037_035_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37657,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ\"","